+## V1.3 — exact MLB algorithm clone activation repair
+
+- Attests the Tennis bootstrap against the exact production MLB winner-engine blob.
+- Preserves the isolated ESPN Tennis result crosswalk and Tennis-only self-training model registry.
+- Floors the earliest-match-minus-10-hours boundary to the prior 15-minute heartbeat so collection never starts late.
+- Removes the deployment-only requirement for a second provider account credential; deployment may inject the existing provider credential only into the isolated `TENNIS_ODDS_API_KEY` runtime variable.
+- Keeps every Tennis table, bucket, Lambda, lock, outcome, model, schedule, log, and metric separate from MLB.
